  <item nodeId="node-307">
    <command xml:space="preserve">z</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Time passes.&#x000A;&#x000A;closeness: 5.&#x000A;You're faster and more maneuverable than they are, but there are more of them.  One charges you directly, and when you veer off to avoid her, another crashes into you.  The rest swarm you instantly.&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;    *** Your luck has run out. ***&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;&#x000A;Would you like to RESTART, RESTORE a saved game, QUIT, or UNDO the last command?&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-308"/>
    </children>
  </item>
