    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-340">
    <command xml:space="preserve">summon mist</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">That's as thick as you can make the mist--there's simply no more water to pull into the air.&#x000A;&#x000A;closeness: 3.&#x000A;The guards charge, but you manage to evade their uncoordinated attack.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
